data.description: Welcome to 10785 Longview Drive located in sought after Grand Bay, Al.  NEW HVAC in (2021),  NEW ROOF (2021) and NEW HOT WATER HEATER (2023). This gorgeous house is three bedroom, two and a half bath creole style home. Close to shopping and just miles to I-10. Leaving the covered front porch you will  enter the home into the large family room boasting a wood burning fireplace, and a half bath. The flooring is split brick continuing  into the kitchen which has stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and an eat in kitchen. The laundry is located off the kitchen and is spacious. The master bedroom is located downstairs with a barn door opening to master from the bedroom and a barn door opening to the massive closet which is off the master bathroom. The other two bedrooms are located upstairs and each has plenty of storage space with walk in closets. The home is situated on a large lot. The back yard is fenced in with a workshop / shed that has a newer metal roof. It has two roll top doors on the front that two vehicles could easily fit in and in the back of the shed there is a work station. Buyer / Buyer's Agent to verify lot dimensions and square footage. Home sold AS-IS with no warranties expressed or implied.  Call your favorite realtor today for a showing as this beauty won't last long!
